pageContext.description: Sand in socket.,Curious herring-bone incisions on sides, within hollows of blade corners. The ribs in socket are very marked & regular & 25mm long.
pageContext.surface: slightly rough, owing to a very slight encrustment of rust colour & green
pageContext.associations: One of a Bronze Founder's Hoard of 16 Socketed Celts & 20 Lumps of Rough Metal also 14 pieces of socketed celts & 14 small pieces of an earthenware pot, 4 pieces of Rim of Burial Urn, a pair of Burial Urn Handles, 3 Spearheads, 1 Chape & part of a Socketed Tool.
